#### 关于 setData

假如你想在 this.setData 的 key 中传入变量，下述写法报错：

```
triggerSelected (e) {
    var dataset = e.target.dataset;
    var id = dataset.id;
    var name = dataset.name;
    var type = dataset.type;
    this.setData({
        selected[type]: {
            id: id,
            name: name
        }
    });
}

```

且 this.setData 不支持模板字符串形式的 key，下述写法也报错：

```
triggerSelected (e) {
    var dataset = e.target.dataset;
    var id = dataset.id;
    var name = dataset.name;
    var type = dataset.type;
    this.setData({
        `selected.${type}`: {
            id: id,
            name: name
        }
    });
}

```

可将 selected 存入变量，直接操作 selected 变量后再 this.setData：

```
triggerSelected (e) {
    var dataset = e.target.dataset;
    var id = dataset.id;
    var name = dataset.name;
    var type = dataset.type;
    var selected = this.data.selected;
    selected[type] = {
        id: id,
        name: name
    };
    this.setData({
        selected: selected
    });
}
```
